    <description><![CDATA[
EditorLint is a lightning-fast EditorConfig checker and auto-fixer written in Go.

## Features

- **Lightning Fast**: Written in Go for maximum performance
- **EditorConfig Support**: Full support for EditorConfig specification
- **Auto-Fix**: Automatically fix common formatting issues
- **Multiple Formats**: Support for various file types
- **Cross-Platform**: Works on Windows, macOS, and Linux

## Usage

```
editorlint [flags] [files...]
```

### Examples

```
# Check all files in current directory
editorlint .

# Check specific files
editorlint file1.txt file2.js

# Auto-fix issues
editorlint --fix .
```

For more information, visit the [project homepage](https://github.com/editorlint/editorlint).
]]></description>
